Dina Spybey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dina_Spybey 0 Dina Spybey (born August 29, 1965) is an American actress. She has appeared in more than 20 films, including John Q., subUrbia and The Haunted Mansion. She is perhaps best known for her role as Tracy Montrose Blair on the first season of Six Feet Under. She played "young Elise Eliot" in The First Wives Club. Dina_Spybey ( born August_29_,_1965 ) is an_American_actress .
